params.ids: array of ids for the tokens to burn

mint(address,uint256,uint256,bytes32).details: this can be a new token or "topping up" the balance of a non-fungible token ID

params.data: the data associated with this mint. Usually stays empty
params.receiver: the account that will receive the minted token

params.ids: array of ids for the tokens
params.receiver: the account that will receive the minted token
